<L>__{exterior high school parking lot later that day}
<A>__{commencement is over the parking lot is a sea of cars slowly negotiating through the mob of celebrating graduates, beaming parents, and rambunctious siblings. as helen slips through the crowd she is pleasantly ambushed by three (second grade) students of hers. she has a brief exchange with the children and then moves on. helen finds herself face to face with lloyd abbott as they both attempt to pass through a narrow space between two parked vehicles. they are both caught off guard there is no graceful way for them to squeeze past each other.}
